Netcdf Data Processing

# Reshape data
pm25_df <- melt(pm25)
pm25_df
pm25_df$lon <- rep(lon, length(lat))
pm25_df$lat <- rep(lat, each = length(lon))
pm25_df
pm25_df <- pm25_df %>% 
  select(-c(Var1, Var2)) %>% 
  rename(pm25 = value) %>% 
  drop_na(pm25)

dim(pm25_df)
[1] 22786140        3
pm25_df
pm25_sf <- st_as_sf(pm25_df, coords = c("lon","lat"))
st_set_crs(pm25_sf, st_crs(grid_sf))
